## anon-connection-wizard (started by whonix-setup-wizard) edits Tor config
## files, therefore needs root.
## For better usability, because otherwise the autostart of whonix-setup-wizard
## at first boot would require password entry.
## Feel free to disable it.
%sudo ALL=NOPASSWD: /usr/bin/whonix-setup-wizard setup
